; Right-rotates the bits of the value at 0x3050 once.
; CSC 225, Assignment 2

; Register Uses: 
; R0: running total 
; R1: counter 
; R2: working value 

0011 0000 0000 0000     ; Start at 0x3000.
0010 000 001001111      ; Load 0x3050 into R0.
0101 001 001 1 00000    ; AND R1 with 0 (clear R1)
0001 001 001 1 01111    ; ADD R1 with #15 (counter of 15)

0000 110 000001000      ; while the last touched register is positive 

0001 010 000 000 000    ; ADD R0 with R0, store in R2
0001 000 000 1 00000    ; ADD R0 with #0  

0000 011 000000001      ; if last touched register is negative 
0001 010 010 1 00001    ; ADD R2 with #1 

0101 000 000 1 00000    ; AND R0 with 0 (clear R0)
0001 000 010 000 000    ; ADD R2 with R0 (put R2 in R0)  
0001 001 001 1 11111    ; ADD R1 with #-1 (decrement the counter)

0000 111 111110111      ; loop back 

0011 000 001000100      ; Store R0 in 0x3051 
1111 0000 00100101      ; Halt.
